Class OperatorContainer

java.lang.Object
  com.igormaznitsa.prol.data.Term
      com.igormaznitsa.prol.containers.OperatorContainer

public final class OperatorContainer
extends Term

The class implements an operator contaier, i.e. the object contains all operators of a knowledge base which have the same names but different types and priorities

Author:
Igor Maznitsa (igor.maznitsa@igormaznitsa.com)
